Nafisah Ahmad Zen Shahab (Arabic: نفیسه أحمد زين شهاب, : ; Arabic pronunciation: [nafiːsah ˈ(ʔ)αmad zajn ʃahaːb]; amụrụ n'August 1, 1946) bụ onye ahịa batik Indonesia si Palemisahbang, South Sumatra

Nafisah bụ nne na-arụ ọrụ dị ka naanị nne n'ezinụlọ ya mgbe di ya, Alwi Idrus Shahab nwụrụ na ọnwa àtó nke Febụwarị, 2010, bụ ncheta nke ndị dọkịta iri, Indonesia, ndị dọketa nke ndị ọkachamara, ndị dọka iri, ndị dọks Indonesia kacha ochie, ndị dọkakịta Indonesia, ndị kasị okenye, ndị dọki iri, ndị Indonesia, ndị India, bụ ndị dọkụ Indonesia, ndị ọkachamara, bụ ndị kasị ochie, ndị India
Idrus Alwi, Sp.PD., K-KV, FECS, FACC.,  bụ ọkachamara n'ihe gbasara obi ma bụrụkwa onye isi oche nke Association of Indonesian Internal Medicine Experts (PB PAPDI) maka oge 2012-2015
